textDisplay: Thank you for being the Greatest Captain we ever had for both Keyakizaka46 and Sakurazaka46. You have no idea how fortunate we feel to have you. I'm so glad that you could be our One and Only Ganbariki Captain and Our One and Only Sugai-sama. You being a Captain, we know you have endured a lot of things. With all your efforts and hard work, this time we wanted to tell you that they have paid off. They always do. You did well and there's no way Keyaki-Saku Buddies won't acknowledge it. Everybody loves Captain Sugai Yuuka.To be honest it has been a turbulent years but for both Happy and Tough times your smile and kind words never fails to calm us down and assure us.Even though it hurts, it's frustrating, and sad to see you go my gratitude and respect weighs more.We hate to see you go and if possible we don't want you to go. Thank you for being the Greatest Captain we ever had for both Keyakizaka46 and Sakurazaka46. You have no idea how fortunate we feel to have you. I'm so glad that you could be our One and Only Ganbariki Captain and Our One and Only Sugai-sama.

Even though it hurts, it's frustrating, and sad to see you go my gratitude and respect weighs more.
